column1: Whoa, we're, uh, really high up...
Look at all those lights... This is pretty exciting.

You can see all of Osaka from up here. Strange to
think we were fighting out there just recently...

I'll bet seeing all of this means a lot more to you
guys now that we've taken down Konoe.
Now if only Owada went down with him...
Oh well, we can leave that to Zenkichi. In the meantime, we should just enjoy the view.
Hey, what's that thing over there?

The shape looks kinda familiar, like maybe it's
got some mystery pockets or something.

...That is the mascot of Tenboto, and its name is 
"Benzaimaru." Praying to it is said to bring one
good luck with money.
Makes sense. A fitting god for a city of commerce.

Inari'd be crying tears of joy if he were here. He
was all bummed about his prize money running
out.

I think I'll go and pray to it myself. Anything to
bring the company success.
I'll go ahead and wish for more modeling gigs.
Are you going to wish for anything, [1B]S1?
Wow, that's quite a sinister smile...
I think I'll wish for that too.
We've come so far. Let's all pray to it together.

I wish that I'll get to walk on a big stage with the
very best of them! And that I'll maybe get some
sweets along the way!

I wish for all of my employees and customers to
always have smiles on their faces...

I wish for Leblanc to be successful... Just not too
busy... *mutter* *mutter*

I wish for Sis and the Phantom Thieves to always
be happy, even in the hardest of times...
ナゼに上から会話した！？
いや呼んじゃダメだろ！
もう...バチが当たるわよ...
絆が深まった気がする...
Come on, you should make a wish too.

Okay, it's almost time for the celebration. We
should get going.
Yeah, it's party time! I found us a good place, so I hope you guys're looking forward to it!
I'm so glad I came here with you...
Thanks for inviting me out today. What should we do next?

...Man, there's a couple everywhere you look.
Guess that makes sense, since it's summer
vacation and all.

The night view and the mood are really nice, too,
so I'm sure it makes for a perfect date spot.

If you were to come here on a date with
someone, who would it be?
Wow, way to toss him a bomb...
I-I'm actually kinda curious about that.
...I wanna know too. Who? Who is it?
But we want to know who that is!
Wait... You mean you have multiple choices!?

Are you saying it's none of us? Come on, give us
some details!

I agree. This is a good opportunity, so I think you
could at least give us a proper answer.
How come everyone's getting so heated...?
Oh man, this might take awhile...
I had an exciting chat with everyone...

It was time to go, so we left to meet up for the
celebration...
